main event: A report of an unidentified flying object in San Bernardino, California on July 19, 1956.
interesting points: The UFO is described as a slightly blurred disk-like shape,The object has a darker bottom and a lighter top, resembling a typical 'flying saucer',The report includes annotations pointing to features of the UFO,There are two photographs included with the report, but they are not visible on the page.
sighted object: unidentified flying object resembling a flying saucer
